<h2 id="section-top">General Medicine</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1431">Lewisham and Greenwich NHS Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">Specialist Medicine Directorate<br/>020 3192 6099</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent857c212a1f684a448e63204b2fd1684e">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Specialist Medicine" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=1850"/>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Lewisham Healthcare NHS Trust provides a wide range of specialist medicine services at University Hospital Lewisham and in the wider community, including cancer screening and treatment, specialist nursing, and respiratory services.</strong></p>
<p>In 2010, the Trust opened a new day care clinic for cancer patients. Based in Riverside, the clinic replaced old fashioned hospital facilities and provides a modern, purpose-built environment for outpatients to receive chemotherapy treatment.</p>
<p>The Trust is also now using state-of-the-art technology to saves lives by detecting coronary heart disease and other life-threatening illnesses more effectively. In 2011, the Trust installed a new CT scanner, to enable doctors to provide more accurate diagnoses quicker than other diagnostic tests, so patients can be given the treatment they need as soon as possible.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>What services are provided by the Specialist Medicine Directorate?</strong></p>
<p>Please click on the following links for further information about the services we provide:</p>
