<p><strong>Further information</strong></p>
<p>For further information, including clinic times, referral details and key staff, please <strong><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/specialist_medicine.aspx">visit the specialist medicine section of our website</a></strong>.</p></div>
